### Component 8: Security Implementation

| Feature | Implementation |
|---|---|
| Auth | JWT (access 15min + refresh 7d) via `python-jose` |
| Passwords | `bcrypt` via `passlib` |
| RBAC | `role` enum on `users` table; FastAPI dependency checks |
| CSRF | CSRF token on state-changing Next.js forms |
| Rate limiting | `slowapi` on FastAPI (100/min per IP default) |
| File uploads | 10MB limit; type validation (PDF only for documents) |
| Antivirus | `clamd` (ClamAV) optional scan on upload |
| Audit logging | `audit_logs` table; populated by admin route middleware |

